{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome all strategy game enthusiasts to the story of &quot;The Three Kingdoms: The Tales of Jian An&quot; This is a very traditional turn-based strategy game. We believe players who enjoy strategy games will find the fun they\u2019re looking for in this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game progresses through &quot;Story Mode&quot; and &quot;Battle Mode.&quot; In Story Mode, you can enjoy an extremely detailed historical story that aligns with the logic of the late Eastern Han period.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362990/extras/1.jpg?t=1734333534\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game is not a strict historical retelling. It does not feature well-known but clich\u00e9 scenes from &quot;Romance of the Three Kingdoms,&quot; like &quot;The Oath of the Peach Garden,&quot; &quot;The Three Heroes vs. L\u00fc Bu,&quot; or &quot;Guan Yu Slays Hua Xiong.&quot; Instead, our story follows the historical records in texts such as &quot;Records of the Three Kingdoms,&quot; &quot;Zizhi Tongjian,&quot; and &quot;Book of the Later Han,&quot; while reasonably expanding and fictionalizing the events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362990/extras/2.jpg?t=1734333534\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the traditional turn-based combat mode, we have also introduced many fresh and interesting attempts and changes, such as the &quot;Fog System,&quot; &quot;Weather System,&quot; and &quot;Time Change System,&quot; adding plenty of new elements to the classic strategy gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362990/extras/3.jpg?t=1734333534\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362990/extras/4.jpg?t=1734333534\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The interesting battlefield completion system and achievement system showcase your control over the battlefield.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362990/extras/5.jpg?t=1734333534\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collecting contents like the &quot;Character Encyclopedia,&quot; &quot;Treasure Encyclopedia,&quot; &quot;Legend Encyclopedia,&quot; &quot;Glossary Appreciation,&quot; and &quot;Music Appreciation&quot; are a great pleasure for completionists.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362990/extras/6.jpg?t=1734333534\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3362990/extras/7.jpg?t=1734333534\" /> Want to experience a completely different Three Kingdoms story, or satisfy your nostalgic love for turn-based strategy games? &quot;The Three Kingdoms: The Tales of Jian An&quot; is your best choice.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"\u521d\u5c1d\u80dc\u679c","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3362990/9b510b4a8340059748469297b79a594be1f8f2e3.jpg"},{"name":"\u82f1\u96c4\u96c6\u7ed3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3362990/9b510b4a8340059748469297b79a594be1f8f2e3.jpg"},{"name":"\u6295\u519b\u4ece\u620e","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3362990/9b510b4a8340059748469297b79a594be1f8f2e3.jpg"},{"name":"\u5c48\u8eab\u86f0\u4f0f","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3362990/9b510b4a8340059748469297b79a594be1f8f2e3.jpg"},{"name":"\u5ba6\u621a\u76f8\u4e89","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3362990/9b510b4a8340059748469